	</div>
</div>
</div>
  <div id="block-cam_search_160" class="block">
  <div class="directory-mini directory-mini-cam">
	<div class="directory-mini-inner">
		<h2>Find Local:</h2>
		<ul>
			<li><a href="http://Acupuncturists.HealthProfs.com/cam/?utm_source=www&utm_medium=link&utm_campaign=left_find_healthprof">Acupuncturists</a></li>
			<li><a href="http://Chiropractors.HealthProfs.com/cam/?utm_source=www&utm_medium=link&utm_campaign=left_find_healthprof">Chiropractors</a></li>
			<li><a href="http://MassageTherapists.HealthProfs.com/cam/?utm_source=www&utm_medium=link&utm_campaign=left_find_healthprof">Massage Therapists</a></li>
			<li><a href="http://Dentists.HealthProfs.com/cam/?utm_source=www&utm_medium=link&utm_campaign=left_find_healthprof">Dentists</a></li>
			<li><a href="http://healthprofs.com/cam/?utm_source=www&utm_medium=link&utm_campaign=left_find_healthprof">and more!</a></li>
		</ul>
		<div class="search-form">
			<form action="http://healthprofs.com/cam/prof_results.php">
